statements: SELECT metric_name, metric_value FROM neural_network_performance_metrics WHERE metric_value > 0.5 ORDER BY metric_value DESC
SELECT * FROM neural_network_performance_metrics WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' ORDER BY timestamp ASC
SELECT metric_name, timestamp FROM neural_network_performance_metrics WHERE metric_value < 0.3 ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT metric_id, metric_name, metric_value FROM neural_network_performance_metrics WHERE metric_name LIKE 'Accuracy%'
SELECT AVG(metric_value) AS avg_metric_value, COUNT(metric_id) AS total_metrics FROM neural_network_performance_metrics
SELECT * FROM neural_network_performance_metrics WHERE metric_value > 0.8 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT metric_name, AVG(metric_value) AS average_value FROM neural_network_performance_metrics GROUP BY metric_name HAVING AVG(metric_value) > 0.5
SELECT metric_name, COUNT(metric_id) AS total_count FROM neural_network_performance_metrics GROUP BY metric_name ORDER BY total_count DESC

SELECT * FROM neural_networks ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT id, name, layers FROM neural_networks WHERE layers > 3;
SELECT * FROM performance_metrics WHERE metric_value > 0.8 ORDER BY metric_value DESC;
SELECT name, activation_function FROM neural_networks WHERE id = 2;
SELECT neural_network_id, metric_name FROM performance_metrics WHERE neural_network_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM neural_networks ORDER BY name DESC, id ASC LIMIT 3
SELECT n.name, p.metric_name, r.report_date FROM neural_networks n JOIN performance_metrics p ON n.id = p.neural_network_id JOIN reports r ON n.id = r.neural_network_id WHERE p.metric_value > 0.5

SELECT n.name, r.report_date, d.decision FROM neural_networks n JOIN reports r ON n.id = r.neural_network_id JOIN decision_making d ON r.id = d.report_id WHERE n.layers > 2 AND d.decision = 'Accept' ORDER BY r.report_date DESC LIMIT 3
SELECT n.name, COUNT(p.metric_name) AS num_metrics FROM neural_networks n LEFT JOIN performance_metrics p ON n.id = p.neural_network_id GROUP BY n.name HAVING num_metrics > 1
SELECT n.name, AVG(p.metric_value) AS avg_metric_value FROM neural_networks n JOIN performance_metrics p ON n.id = p.neural_network_id GROUP BY n.name HAVING AVG(p.metric_value) > 0.3
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkMetrics ORDER BY date_recorded DESC;
